[02.12.15] When I moved to another school when I was elementary, I was so afraid of new environment. I ever skip my course because of the fear of new environment. I'm not good at making friend. I'm not good at telling everyone who I am. The same thing happened in junior and senior high school. I was only making friends with my classmate and all I know is my classmate and several persons who ever be my classmate. I don't have any friend surround my house. I'm that bad in making friends indeed. At the time I have to fly to Bandung to continue my study, you have to know how afraid I was. I was all alone because I'm the one who enter the university from my school. Time flies, I've past my elementary school, finished my course, graduated from junior and senior high school and made some friends in my fresh year in college. I have such a bad manner, lot of lack and thousand reasons to be not friended by anyone. But there are still lot of people stand with me, give me support, give me smile, accept my lack, grow better with me, even share their life with me. I still wonder how? All I know I have never tried hard to make friend with someone. I have never tried to be another person just to make a friend. I realise, they're there not because of me. But God does send them to me to coloring my life. Today's blessing is : friends, lot of friends and those who always stand with me. #blessedecember #lilyandrosedecemberchallenge

caption.text: Our 15 years togetherness without being separated more than  4 days is over in this day where I had my college registration and validation. I have to be honest that it is really hard to be apart with someone whom you used to spend your time with. I used to walk alone in Bandung. Going home alone, eating food alone, shopping stuffs alone and many more just because he is not here. I used to refuse people who want to give me ride with, "aku dijemput amos kok". But now, I refuse people with, "selow ae udah biasa balik sendiri". I'm not asking people to give me ride or accompany me to somewhere I want to go. I just want him to be here. Not anybody else. I'm going to cry realizing this year I'm not there to celebrate his birthday anymore. I don't sent him any present either. I just want to be there to give cake and see him blow the candle. I'm missing you from another island, birthday boy. Happy birthday, my big lilbro😢😢😢😢😭😭😭

Kini sudah saatnya slayer itu dilepaskan. Bukan karena ini berakhir. Namun karena sesuatu yang lain tengah menanti.

caption.text: Drink this because of missing someone.

Someone is turning 19 today. We were in different senior high school but she's one of two that used to come to my home without any permission. Disturbing my nap time, my me-time,  watching me having nap, snapping every bad photos of mine while taking nap, and so on. She (plus mirza) never mind if they come and find there's no me at home. We used to fight during junior high school. Yelling each other, not talk each other, and end ut by forgiving each other. Now, we're not only in different campus but also province and island. No coming to home during my nap time, no disturbing my me-time, no snapping my ugly nap face anymore. I wish I could swim accross the ocean and bring you cake with candle on it, singing happy birthday to you and eat the cake with you. But the only thing I can do is, chat you and type "happy birthday" and give you bunch of wishes. Happy birthday, Debi. Believe me, I'm missing you from thousand kilometers away😭😭😭 thank you for growing up with me since our junior high, let's grow until our last breath and keep supporting each other. Have a tons of blast, Bi!😊

caption.text:
"TVST ga bakal terasa sama lagi" - Ahmad, ca-himafi dan belum dilantik.
.
.
.
Perform itu pilihan ketiga. Pilihan pertama itu keamanan. Entah bagaimana caranya tapi kelempar ke perform. Kenapa ga protes ke msdm? Karena gatau kalau bisa protes. Tapi seneng karena di perform bisa balik sebulan full. Sedih sih ga ikutan bukber tapi yha ku bahagia bisa pulang. Kirain perform gabut. Kirain...ternyata perform itu nonlap berasa panlap:') lelah bgtbgtan harus olahrasa tiap hari dan bisa lbh dari sejam. Dari yang kuda-kuda ngerasa sakit di seluruh badan, plank ga bisa lurus badannya, teriak-teriak karena tiba-tiba ada gerak khayang dan teriak-teriak karena malu setiap diliatin orang-orang sampai kuda-kuda ga asik kalau cuman 100, tanpa disuruh udah plank aja, waktu adegan berantem otomatis khayang dan seneng kalau bisa olah rasa di depan orang ramai.
.
.
Pergi pagi pulangnya pagi juga tiap hari. Dingin-dinginan tiap malam. Kaos kaki rusak semua sampai ga pake kaos kaki lagi kalau perform. Kaki luka setiap harinya karena mijak bata-bata kasar di jalanan sekitar oktagon. Baju dan rambut selalu kotor dengan debu tvst, oktagon ataupun labtek VI lt. 2. Sensasi kena lem korea paling gabisa dilupain. Begitu juga dengan jarum yang nusuk dan nempel di tangan. Handsaplast yang baru dibeli habis gitu aja. Ada goresan luka di kali sama tangan ntah darimana pasti ada aja. Guling-gulingan di saraga, neriakin maba dan medik, trus jadi hobi nyanyi lagu iklan biji selasih padahal belum pernah nonton. Dua bulan lebih di perform ngabisin banyak duit, tenaga dan waktu. Tapi pas closing lagunya mati. Sedih sih, tapi bangga karena latihan dua bulan lebih itu ga sia sia karena kami tetap bahagia dan menikmati. Latihan sampai lewat dari jam 12 padahal udah H-1 di saraga ga boleh dilupain banget. Guling-guling di saraga juga ga boleh dilupain. Dinginnya rumput saraga yang basah juga. Ternyata pasir saraga yang basah lebih buruk dari kejijikan apapun yang pernah ada.
.
.
.
Kesimpulan dari semuanya adalah..being part of perform OSKM ITB 15, is an honor and one of the unforgetable moment. Thank you, seribu gurat merah di langit senja!
